725091f-a.title: Queens: 20th Avenue - 124th Street
725091f-a.text:
20th Avenue (right), at the N.E. corner of 124th Street.
The corner house was owned, in 1873, by H. Knerr, and the one
on the extrenne right by F. Hunold. 20th Avenue was then named
5th Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  March 16, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS
